      <title>投资者为秘鲁 70 亿美元养老金提款法案做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/investors-brace-for-7-billion-pension-withdrawal-bill-in-peru</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者担心，一项允许秘鲁人动用退休储蓄的提案可能会迫使养老基金出售资产，以便提取多达 70 亿美元的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/investors-brace-for-7-billion-pension-withdrawal-bill-in-peru</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 20:15:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马自达首席执行官谈供应链问题、电动汽车采用、美国销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-09/mazda-ceo-on-supply-chain-issues-ev-adoption-us-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马自达汽车公司总裁兼首席执行官 Masahiro Moro 谈论了因巴尔的摩 Key Bridge 倒塌、电动汽车普及缓慢、来自中国的竞争以及扩大在美国业务而引起的供应链问题。他在“彭博市场：收盘”中发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-09/mazda-ceo-on-supply-chain-issues-ev-adoption-us-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 20:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>不列颠哥伦比亚省三年内第三次信用评级下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/british-columbia-gets-third-credit-downgrade-in-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不列颠哥伦比亚省的信用评级被标普全球评级下调至 AA-，展望为负面——三年内第三次降级——省政府决定增加借贷后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/british-columbia-gets-third-credit-downgrade-in-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 17:43:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Diamondback 为 Endeavour 交易出售 55 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/diamondback-kicks-off-bond-sale-to-help-fund-endeavor-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Diamondback Energy Inc. 在美国投资级市场借款 55 亿美元，为其以 260 亿美元收购 Endeavor Energy Resources LP 提供部分资金，与其他蓝筹公司一起利用强劲的投资者需求进行与收购相关的债务交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/diamondback-kicks-off-bond-sale-to-help-fund-endeavor-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 15:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在 CPI 数据公布之前，新兴股市攀升至 2022 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/emerging-stock-index-heads-for-highest-close-in-nearly-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场股市收于 2022 年 6 月以来的最高水平，交易员正在为本周的美国通胀数据做好准备，以衡量美联储下一步的货币政策举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/emerging-stock-index-heads-for-highest-close-in-nearly-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 07:45:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
